      "module_path": "dry_check::interactor",
      "docs": "Implements `DryCheckService`. Updated for D3 (parallel fan-out with DryCheckParallelism limit from DryCheckConfig), D4 (run-level two-tier calibration barrier: fast-tier production results stay provisional until known-bad probes pass; fast calibration failure discards provisional results and rejudges every production pair on the final tier before appending records), and D5 (writes DryCheckCoverageRecord including corpus_fingerprint after completing all judgments, so DryCheckApprovalInteractor can detect corpus changes). Holds injected port dependencies, track_id, config, config_fingerprint, and corpus_fingerprint as private fields.",
